['DescriptionLime House Real Estate Broker is pleased to offer a 1 bedroom apartment with a very large balcony on a low floor for sale in Azizi Feirouz, Al Furjan:
Property details:
- Balcony surrounding the apartment is of 90.69 sqm (976.19 sqft);
- Living room and dining area is well-shaped with no odd corner;
- 1 large bedroom with en-suite bathroom;
- Fully equipped and fitted kitchen; 
- Separate powder-room (toilet);
- Internal community view;
- 1 dedicated covered  parking; 
Investment/Personal-use points to consider:
Asking Price: AED 900,000 (slightly negotiable);
Currently Leased till April 2020 for AED 70,000 (1 cheque) (as provided by Landlord);
Service Charges (estimates based on DLD website): AED 14.41/sqft
ORN: 16923, BRN:44412;
Permit Number: 30028;
About Azizi Feirouz:
With a view of the enchanting Dubai Marina skyscrapers from the Al Furjan community setting, the Azizi Feirouz Residence is uniquely positioned.
For any further queries and viewings, contact us on +971582161314.']
